      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 10 judgment</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 10 judgment</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>履虎尾，不咥人，亨。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>(Lu suggests the idea of) one treading on the tail of a tiger, which does not bite him. There will be progress and success.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
