      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 10 九二</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 10 九二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九二，履道坦坦，幽人貞吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second NINE, undivided, shows its subject treading the path that is level and easy - a quiet and solitary man, to whom, if he be firm and correct, there will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
