      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 10 九四</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九四，履虎尾，愬愬終吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth NINE, undivided, shows its subject treading on the tail of a tiger. He becomes full of apprehensive caution, and in the end there will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
