      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 10 九五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九五，夬履，貞厲。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth NINE, undivided, shows the resolute tread of its subject. Though he be firm and correct, there will be peril.</seg>
      </tuv>
