      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 10 上九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 10 上九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>上九，視履考祥，其旋元吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The sixth NINE, undivided, tells us to look at (the whole course) that is trodden, and examine the presage which that gives. If it be complete and without failure, there will be great good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
